reviewText:
This DVD shows how to use the bar it comes with.

It shows how to use the bar standing, reclining, sitting or laying down.  To work the legs, abs, glutes, back, shoulders, chests, arms and neck.

This DVD demonstrates resistance training nicely.
I love this DVD personal Training Workout. He is so fun to workout with. The workout is fun and does work nicely.

My daughter gave me an easy shaper but I lost the DVD when traveling.  The seller was prompt in sending me the DVD.  Since I had knee surgery I will use the dvd again, once I'm given the ok from my surgeon.

I only thought I was buying the DVD since I had the easy shaper unit.  But I received everything.
Both were in excellent condition and arrived very quickly.  I couldn't be more pleased.
